{"tid":2218171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「朋友tinder中咗網上情騙搵同類受害者希望集合報案」","createTime":"2020-09-26T04:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T11:37:35.000Z","uid":103382,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"90f2de3a03373f215ecef02eadb4355b59a482ce","tid":2218171,"uid":103382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:41:50.000Z","msg":"事源佢係tinder識咗個男人 然後交換WhatsApps繼續發展<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就開始氹我朋友玩 bitcoin 同個啲咩coincola。個騙徒教佢去第三方平台投資（亞博網上平台）。一開頭有小小甜頭，到比大數個陣想拎翻錢就開始出問題，不停要我朋友再入錢，用黎解鎖認證之類，我朋友就覺得唔可以再放錢落去錢贖錢，而家就拎唔翻啲錢。之後騙徒一直堅持佢無教唆又唔消失，以致報警調查滯停，因為啲狗話個騙徒一日唔消失，一日都唔叫呃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人或朋友有類似經歷 可以集合一齊去報案 增加破案機會<br />\n<br />\n要話事主蠢就預咗，希望大家屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋屌還屌 希望大家可以集結到更多受害者一齊去解決、追討<br />\n最緊要係避免更多人受害<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1f2c0e9db2ef57674648c2a7e760408af56f2d8","tid":2218171,"uid":45749,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:44:18.000Z","msg":"呢啲冇得追<br />\n你情我願<br />\n報狗都唔會理<br />\n錢少就當買教訓<br />\n錢多就下世小心啲"},{"pid":"ee01d41754e381a997f192a18eae58c657d3aed7","tid":2218171,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"點解唔消失就唔算呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d863709a7b82e0ace813c4d3b20c61f3eec27a","tid":2218171,"uid":157525,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:44:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">你的朋友就是你</span></span><br />\n你同班狗講 個男人叫你買0282 咁佢地就會即刻拉人架啦"},{"pid":"5b03f1a2aa5010b124a7f5b66ccf11c953e19b78","tid":2218171,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:46:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15234008cb2f49db537d34a15012fe18baf96a7f","tid":2218171,"uid":103382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee01d41754e381a997f192a18eae58c657d3aed7","tid":2218171,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"點解唔消失就唔算呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"因為佢話個網站又無消失，個騙徒又無消失，無得確定筆錢係拎唔翻，所以唔會幫我朋友落案查，如果一陣查咗又拎得翻，就浪費警方資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d11850c0a26409ba88c1e79d526355133aad907","tid":2218171,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:52:24.000Z","msg":"幫唔到，人地早有預謀"},{"pid":"0bc833b2f59bd08c5b23df68326aba21628bf28f","tid":2218171,"uid":92064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:54:33.000Z","msg":"幾多先<br />\n5萬內算啦，浪費時間"},{"pid":"56f2c71be80f6acc11fbdd9f4534a13bff958bd9","tid":2218171,"uid":103382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bc833b2f59bd08c5b23df68326aba21628bf28f","tid":2218171,"uid":92064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:54:33.000Z","msg":"幾多先<br />\n5萬內算啦，浪費時間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:00:50.000Z","msg":"好似話都六位數"},{"pid":"287e1b5afb0c5a5844f1f836800ad5cb5e81d204","tid":2218171,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:03:35.000Z","msg":"我建議你去FB 出post<br />\n將成件事貼晒出來<br />\n如果出對方容貌要打格"},{"pid":"7299877e6d873f1653f41a7004f185960167d3be","tid":2218171,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"身騎白馬今次扮美軍定ibanker"},{"pid":"8d6b1c59be75